29#include <gelf.h>
30#include <libelf.h>
31#include <string.h>
32
33#include "_libelf.h"
34
35__RCSID("$NetBSD: gelf_xlate.c,v 1.3 2016/02/20 02:43:42 christos Exp $");
36ELFTC_VCSID("Id: gelf_xlate.c 3174 2015-03-27 17:13:41Z emaste ");
37
38Elf_Data *
39elf32_xlatetof(Elf_Data *dst, const Elf_Data *src, unsigned int encoding)
40{
41 return _libelf_xlate(dst, src, encoding, ELFCLASS32, ELF_TOFILE);
42}
43
44Elf_Data *
45elf64_xlatetof(Elf_Data *dst, const Elf_Data *src, unsigned int encoding)
46{
47 return _libelf_xlate(dst, src, encoding, ELFCLASS64, ELF_TOFILE);
48}
49
50Elf_Data *
51elf32_xlatetom(Elf_Data *dst, const Elf_Data *src, unsigned int encoding)
52{
53 return _libelf_xlate(dst, src, encoding, ELFCLASS32, ELF_TOMEMORY);
54}
55
56Elf_Data *
57elf64_xlatetom(Elf_Data *dst, const Elf_Data *src, unsigned int encoding)
58{
59 return _libelf_xlate(dst, src, encoding, ELFCLASS64, ELF_TOMEMORY);
60}
61
62Elf_Data *
63gelf_xlatetom(Elf *e, Elf_Data *dst, const Elf_Data *src,
64 unsigned int encoding)
65{
66 if (e != NULL)
67 return (_libelf_xlate(dst, src, encoding, e->e_class,
68 ELF_TOMEMORY));
69 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
70 return (NULL);
71}
72
73Elf_Data *
74gelf_xlatetof(Elf *e, Elf_Data *dst, const Elf_Data *src,
75 unsigned int encoding)
76{
77 if (e != NULL)
78 return (_libelf_xlate(dst, src, encoding, e->e_class,
79 ELF_TOFILE));
80 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
81 return (NULL);
82}
